+corrupt-filter-memcg
+
+Limit injection to pages owned by memgroup. Specified by inode number
+of the memcg.
+
+Example:
+        mkdir /cgroup/hwpoison
+
+        usemem -m 100 -s 1000 &
+        echo `jobs -p` > /cgroup/hwpoison/tasks
+
